A British man has been sentenced to six months in prison by a Dubai court for pinching a woman's bottom in a bar.

Businessman Steven Sherriff, 43, was sentenced in his absence after being accused of groping a 23-year-old whilst on a bar crawl.

The investor, who lived in Dubai for seven years, was punched unconscious by the woman's livid boyfriend after also allegedly touching the woman between her legs.

