Earlier this year, a British businesswoman was accused of having drunken sex in the back of a Dubai taxi.

Rebecca Blake, 29, from Dorking, Surrey, was sacked from her £100,000 a year job as a recruitment consultant after her alleged tryst with Irish welder Conor McRedmond.

Foreigners jailed in Dubai are deported immediately after completing their sentences.

